---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Documentation | Agentic Nervous System">
  <section class="py-12 sm:py-16 md:py-20">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
      <h1 class="font-display text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-[var(--color-text-primary)] mb-4 sm:mb-6">
        Documentation
      </h1>
      <p class="text-lg sm:text-xl text-[var(--color-text-secondary)] max-w-3xl mb-10 sm:mb-16">
        Comprehensive guides for the Agentic Nervous System. From quick starts to deep technical references.
      </p>
      
      <div class="grid gap-6 sm:gap-8 lg:grid-cols-2">
        <!-- Quick Start -->
        <a href="https://github.com/Mnehmos/mnehmos.multi-agent.framework/blob/main/templates/quick-start.md" class="block bg-[var(--color-bg-surface)] rounded-2xl border border-[var(--color-border-default)] p-6 sm:p-8 hover:border-[var(--color-brand-primary)] hover:shadow-md transition-all">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 sm:gap-4 mb-3 sm:mb-4">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 sm:w-12 sm:h-12 bg-[var(--color-brand-primary)]/20 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-xl sm:text-2xl">ðŸš€</div>
            <div>
              <h2 class="font-display text-lg sm:text-xl font-semibold text-[var(--color-text-primary)]">Quick Start</h2>
              <span class="text-xs text-[var(--color-text-muted)] uppercase tracking-wide">5 min read</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="text-[var(--color-text-secondary)] text-sm sm:text-base">Get the framework running in your IDE. Copy-paste setup for Roo Code, Cursor, Claude Code, and Copilot.</p>
        </a>
        
        <!-- Core Concepts -->
        <a href="https://github.com/Mnehmos/mnehmos.multi-agent.framework/blob/main/README.md" class="block bg-[var(--color-bg-surface)] rounded-2xl border border-[var(--color-border-default)] p-6 sm:p-8 hover:border-[var(--color-brand-primary)] hover:shadow-md transition-all">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 sm:gap-4 mb-3 sm:mb-4">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 sm:w-12 sm:h-12 bg-purple-100 dark:bg-purple-900/30 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-xl sm:text-2xl">ðŸ§ </div>
            <div>
              <h2 class="font-display text-lg sm:text-xl font-semibold text-[var(--color-text-primary)]">Core Concepts</h2>
              <span class="text-xs text-[var(--color-text-muted)] uppercase tracking-wide">10 min read</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="text-[var(--color-text-secondary)] text-sm sm:text-base">Understand the nervous system architecture, layer model, and contract-driven design principles.</p>
        </a>
        
        <!-- Mode Reference -->
        <a href="/mnehmos.multi-agent.framework/team" class="block bg-[var(--color-bg-surface)] rounded-2xl border border-[var(--color-border-default)] p-6 sm:p-8 hover:border-[var(--color-brand-primary)] hover:shadow-md transition-all">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 sm:gap-4 mb-3 sm:mb-4">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 sm:w-12 sm:h-12 bg-amber-100 dark:bg-amber-900/30 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-xl sm:text-2xl">ðŸ‘¥</div>
            <div>
              <h2 class="font-display text-lg sm:text-xl font-semibold text-[var(--color-text-primary)]">Mode Reference</h2>
              <span class="text-xs text-[var(--color-text-muted)] uppercase tracking-wide">Reference</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="text-[var(--color-text-secondary)] text-sm sm:text-base">Detailed documentation for all 13 specialized modes. Capabilities, constraints, and usage patterns.</p>
        </a>
        
        <!-- MCP Integration -->
        <a href="/mnehmos.multi-agent.framework/tools" class="block bg-[var(--color-bg-surface)] rounded-2xl border border-[var(--color-border-default)] p-6 sm:p-8 hover:border-[var(--color-brand-primary)] hover:shadow-md transition-all">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 sm:gap-4 mb-3 sm:mb-4">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 sm:w-12 sm:h-12 bg-blue-100 dark:bg-blue-900/30 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-xl sm:text-2xl">ðŸ”§</div>
            <div>
              <h2 class="font-display text-lg sm:text-xl font-semibold text-[var(--color-text-primary)]">MCP Integration</h2>
              <span class="text-xs text-[var(--color-text-muted)] uppercase tracking-wide">Reference</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="text-[var(--color-text-secondary)] text-sm sm:text-base">How to integrate Model Context Protocol tools with the framework. OODA, Synch, Index Foundry, and Trace.</p>
        </a>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Technical Deep Dives -->
      <h2 class="font-display text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold text-[var(--color-text-primary)] mt-10 sm:mt-16 mb-6 sm:mb-8">Technical Deep Dives</h2>
      
      <div class="grid gap-4 sm:gap-6 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3">
        <a href="https://github.com/Mnehmos/mnehmos.multi-agent.framework/blob/main/templates/custom-instructions-for-all-modes.md" class="block bg-[var(--color-bg-elevated)] rounded-xl border border-[var(--color-border-default)] p-5 sm:p-6 hover:border-[var(--color-text-muted)] transition-colors">
          <h3 class="font-display text-base sm:text-lg font-semibold text-[var(--color-text-primary)] mb-2">Contract System</h3>
          <p class="text-[var(--color-text-secondary)] text-xs sm:text-sm">Runs, steps, boomerang protocol, and parallel safety guarantees.</p>
        </a>
        
        <a href="https://github.com/Mnehmos/mnehmos.multi-agent.framework/blob/main/templates/custom_modes.yaml" class="block bg-[var(--color-bg-elevated)] rounded-xl border border-[var(--color-border-default)] p-5 sm:p-6 hover:border-[var(--color-text-muted)] transition-colors">
          <h3 class="font-display text-base sm:text-lg font-semibold text-[var(--color-text-primary)] mb-2">Mode Definitions</h3>
          <p class="text-[var(--color-text-secondary)] text-xs sm:text-sm">YAML specification for all 13 modes with layer mappings.</p>
        </a>
        
        <a href="https://github.com/Mnehmos/mnehmos.multi-agent.framework/blob/main/templates/universal/AGENTS.md" class="block bg-[var(--color-bg-elevated)] rounded-xl border border-[var(--color-border-default)] p-5 sm:p-6 hover:border-[var(--color-text-muted)] transition-colors">
          <h3 class="font-display text-base sm:text-lg font-semibold text-[var(--color-text-primary)] mb-2">AGENTS.md Standard</h3>
          <p class="text-[var(--color-text-secondary)] text-xs sm:text-sm">Universal agent configuration that works across all IDEs.</p>
        </a>
        
        <a href="https://github.com/Mnehmos/mnehmos.multi-agent.framework/blob/main/templates/tools/ooda-mcp.md" class="block bg-[var(--color-bg-elevated)] rounded-xl border border-[var(--color-border-default)] p-5 sm:p-6 hover:border-[var(--color-text-muted)] transition-colors">
          <h3 class="font-display text-base sm:text-lg font-semibold text-[var(--color-text-primary)] mb-2">OODA MCP Deep Dive</h3>
          <p class="text-[var(--color-text-secondary)] text-xs sm:text-sm">62 tools for computer automation. Complete API reference.</p>
        </a>
        
        <a href="https://github.com/Mnehmos/mnehmos.multi-agent.framework/blob/main/templates/tools/synch-mcp.md" class="block bg-[var(--color-bg-elevated)] rounded-xl border border-[var(--color-border-default)] p-5 sm:p-6 hover:border-[var(--color-text-muted)] transition-colors">
          <h3 class="font-display text-base sm:text-lg font-semibold text-[var(--color-text-primary)] mb-2">Synch MCP Deep Dive</h3>
          <p class="text-[var(--color-text-secondary)] text-xs sm:text-sm">Memory persistence, agent coordination, and context handoff.</p>
        </a>
        
        <a href="https://github.com/Mnehmos/mnehmos.multi-agent.framework/blob/main/templates/tools/index-foundry-mcp.md" class="block bg-[var(--color-bg-elevated)] rounded-xl border border-[var(--color-border-default)] p-5 sm:p-6 hover:border-[var(--color-text-muted)] transition-colors">
          <h3 class="font-display text-base sm:text-lg font-semibold text-[var(--color-text-primary)] mb-2">Index Foundry Deep Dive</h3>
          <p class="text-[var(--color-text-secondary)] text-xs sm:text-sm">RAG pipelines, chunking strategies, and semantic search.</p>
        </a>
      </div>
      
      <!-- GitHub Resources -->
      <div class="mt-10 sm:mt-16 bg-[var(--color-footer-bg)] rounded-2xl p-6 sm:p-8">
        <h2 class="font-display text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold text-stone-50 mb-4 sm:mb-6">GitHub Resources</h2>
        <div class="grid gap-4 sm:gap-6 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3">
          <a href="https://github.com/Mnehmos/mnehmos.multi-agent.framework" class="block bg-[var(--color-bg-elevated)] rounded-xl p-4 sm:p-5 hover:bg-[var(--color-bg-muted)] transition-colors">
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-stone-50 mb-1 text-sm sm:text-base">Main Repository</h3>
            <p class="text-[var(--color-footer-text)] text-xs sm:text-sm">Framework source, templates, and documentation.</p>
          </a>
          
          <a href="https://github.com/Mnehmos/mnehmos.multi-agent.framework/issues" class="block bg-[var(--color-bg-elevated)] rounded-xl p-4 sm:p-5 hover:bg-[var(--color-bg-muted)] transition-colors">
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-stone-50 mb-1 text-sm sm:text-base">Issue Tracker</h3>
            <p class="text-[var(--color-footer-text)] text-xs sm:text-sm">Report bugs or request features.</p>
          </a>
          
          <a href="https://github.com/Mnehmos/mnehmos.multi-agent.framework/discussions" class="block bg-[var(--color-bg-elevated)] rounded-xl p-4 sm:p-5 hover:bg-[var(--color-bg-muted)] transition-colors">
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-stone-50 mb-1 text-sm sm:text-base">Discussions</h3>
            <p class="text-[var(--color-footer-text)] text-xs sm:text-sm">Ask questions and share ideas.</p>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
